TML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":7,"is_redacted":false},{"id":"7cea557276c271a2ede11496ef862521","from":"Helen Kim","from_email":"hkim@nysgmail.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Spam: For Mr. Jeffrey Epstein-MICHAEL CLAYTON","date":"2007-09-21T19:14:36.000Z","formatted_date":"Sep 21, 2007","formatted_time":"7:14 PM","body":" \n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Peggy Siegal [mailto:peggy@peggysiegal.com] \nSent: Friday, September 21, 2007 3:10 PM\nTo: Helen Kim\nSubject: Spam: For Mr. Jeffrey Epstein-MICHAEL CLAYTON\n\n \n\n \n<http://rs6.net/on.jsp?t=1101820014138.0.1101430287919.5416&ts=S0280&o=h\nttp://ui.constantcontact.com/images/p1x1.gif> \n\nPlease come join George Clooney, Tilda Swinton and Tony Gilroy at their\nintimate private screening of Michael Clayton. No red carpet, no\npaparazzi, no press. Its just a terrific low key Sunday night with the\nfilmmakers and their friends.\n\n \n\nxxoo\n\nPeggy\n\n \n\n \n\nWarner Bros. Pictures \n\nSamuels Media and Castle Rock Entertainment\n\n \n\ninvite you to join\n\nGeorge Clooney   Tilda Swinton\n\nand writer and director Tony Gilroy\n\n \n\nat a private screening of\n\nMICHAEL CLAYTON\n\n \n\nSunday, September 30, 2007\n\n \n\n7:00pm The Time Warner Theater\n\nOne Time Warner Center, 10th floor\n\nenter at 58th Street between 8th & 9th Avenues\n\n \n\n9:00pm dinner hosted by Edmiston & Company\n\n \n\nNicholas Edmiston, Chairman\n\n&\n\nDiego Marroquin, Vice President\n\nPorter House New York\n\n10 Columbus Circle, 4th floor\n\n \n\npeggy@peggysiegal.com or 212-935-6700\n\nthis invitation is non-transferable\n\n \n\nMichael Clayton (GEORGE CLOONEY) is an in-house fixer at one of the\nlargest corporate law firms in New York.  A former criminal prosecutor,\nClayton takes care of Kenner, Bach & Ledeens dirtiest work at the behest\nof the firms co-founder Marty Bach (SYDNEY POLLACK).  Though burned out\nand hardly content with his job, his divorce, a failed business venture\nand mounting debt have left Clayton inextricably tied to the firm.  \n\n \n\n            At U/North, meanwhile, the career of litigator Karen Crowder\n(TILDA SWINTON) rests on the multi-million dollar settlement of a class\naction suit that Claytons firm is leading to a seemingly successful\nconclusion.  But when Kenner Bachs brilliant and guilt-ridden attorney\nArthur Edens (TOM WILKINSON) sabotages the U/North case, Clayton faces\nthe biggest challenge of his career and his life.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&m=1101430287919&se=5416&t\n=1101820014138<=en&reason=F> \n\nThis email was sent to hkim@nysgmail.com, by peggy@peggysiegal.com\n\nUpdate Profile/Email Address\n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=oo&m=1101430287919&se=5416&t\n=1101820014138<=en&reason=F>  | Instant removal with SafeUnsubscribe\n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&m=1101430287919&se=5416&t\n=1101820014138<=en&reason=F> (tm) | Privacy Policy\n<http://ui.constantcontact.com/roving/CCPrivacyPolicy.jsp> .\n\n \n\n\nPeggy Siegal | 4 West 58th Street | mezzanine | New York | NY | 10019 \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 11 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<title>Please come join George Clooney, Tilda Swinton and Tony Gilroy at their\nintimate private screening of Michael Clayton</title>\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @fo